      "text": [
        " سَمِعْتُهُ یَقُولُ أَکْثِرُوا مِنَ التَّهْلِیلِ وَ التَّکْبِیرِ فَإِنَّهُ لَیْسَ شَیْ ءٌ أَحَبَّ إِلَی اللَّهِ مِنَ التَّکْبِیرِ وَ التَّهْلِیلِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "13.  Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a.s.) says, “Recite Tahleel (Laa ilaaha illallaah)  and takbeer (Allaahu  Akbar)  often because Allah likes nothing more than Takbeer and Tahleel.”"
